"Com"?
That's probably a really old version you're using, Axoloti does not use a virtual com port since quite a while.
Please check here for latest releases:
https://github.com/axoloti/axoloti/releases
Sorry 1.0.2 for Windows was not released, but 1.03 will follow tonight.
